OL,3,CCampaigners to appeal decision to
OL,4,Cdecline a fresh inquest into
OL,5,CSummerland fire
OL,7,FA lawyer representing the 'Justice for
OL,8,FSummerland' campaign has written to
OL,9,Fthe Isle of Man Attorney General,
OL,10,Fsaying campaigners will be appealing
OL,11,Fhis decision to deny families a fresh
OL,12,Finquest.
OL,14,FDarragh Mackin sent a letter to the
OL,15,FIsle of Man Government's legal advisor
OL,16,Fchallenging his decision to refuse new
OL,17,Finquests into the 50 people who died
OL,18,Fin the fire.
