OL,5,CSummerland fire
OL,7,FThe challenge is grounded in what
OL,8,FPhoenix Law is describing as 'multiple
OL,9,Falleged misdirections in law and
OL,10,Fprocedural irregularities'.
OL,12,FPhoenix Law has issued Pre-Action
OL,13,FProtocol correspondence ahead of
OL,14,Flodging a Petition of Doleance
OL,15,F(judicial review) challenging the
OL,16,FAttorney General's decision.
