OL,3,CCampaigners to appeal decision to
OL,4,Cdecline a fresh inquest into
OL,5,CSummerland fire
OL,7,FWithin the letter, he outlined a
OL,8,Fnumber of reasons for the appeal
OL,9,Fincluding a 'misdirection in law' on
OL,10,Fthe Attorney General's refusal, and
OL,11,Femphasised the 'desirability' for
OL,12,Finquests to be held.
OL,14,FIt comes after Walter Wannenburgh
OL,15,Fdeclined an application to hold a new
OL,16,Finquest into those who died in the
OL,17,FSummerland fire.
OL,19,FCampaigners are fighting to overturn
OL,20,Fthe 'misadventure' verdict placed on
OL,21,Fthe victims of the fire.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
