OL,3,CCampaigners to appeal decision to
OL,4,Cdecline a fresh inquest into
OL,5,CSummerland fire
OL,7,FA total of 50 people died, and 80 more
OL,8,Fwere seriously injured, after a fire
OL,9,Fspread through the island's leisure
OL,10,Fcomplex on 2 August 1973.
OL,12,FIt was, at the time, the worst
OL,13,Fpeacetime loss of life in a fire
OL,14,Fdisaster since the blitz, and many who
OL,15,Fsuffered feel a sense of injustice
OL,16,Faround the tragedy.
OL,18,FTwo commemorative services were held
OL,19,Fover the weekend to mark 52 years
OL,20,Fsince the disaster.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
