OL,3,CCampaigners to appeal decision to
OL,4,Cdecline a fresh inquest into
OL,5,CSummerland fire
OL,7,FDouglas City Council hosted their
OL,8,Fannual ceremony at the Summerland
OL,9,Fmemorial, while campaigners gathered
OL,10,Fat what remains of the Summerland site.
OL,12,FThose fighting for a fresh inquest
OL,13,Fsaid: "The Isle of Man Government has
OL,14,Fhad the chance to right this
OL,15,Fmiscarriage of justice, however the
OL,16,FAttorney General has made the
OL,17,Fdisgraceful decision not to do so. Our
OL,18,Fpursuit of justice continues."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
