OL,7,FMr Mackin has asked for a reply from
OL,8,Fthe Attorney General by 17:00 on 11
OL,9,FAugust.
OL,11,FThe Isle of Man Government declined to
OL,12,Fcomment on the issue, or the 52nd
OL,13,Fanniversary of the Summerland fire.
